room_title: Escape room "The Disappearance at Fogmore Manor" by The Entrapment in San Diego
room_address: 7990 Dagget St. Suite A-10, San Diego, CA, 92111
room_description: You wake up dazed in a dark living room. How did you get here, and where is your business partner? As the wind echoes through the abandoned manor, you search through the ancient relics and find a note from your partner. Can you untangle the web of clues and rescue your partner? When the clock strikes midnight, the evil spirits of this house will be unleashed...
